    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和混合元素以触发反应并解决谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198460/extras/7b097ed6158d8ec4a6d7caedde206378.poster.avif?t=1734144758\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198460/extras/7b097ed6158d8ec4a6d7caedde206378.webm?t=1734144758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198460/extras/7b097ed6158d8ec4a6d7caedde206378.mp4?t=1734144758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索独特的机制：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从表面上看，元素逻辑中的机制似乎很简单。然而，随着每一个新机制都建立在旧机制之上并与旧机制交织在一起，谜题很快就会变得复杂而有趣。要完成游戏，您需要掌握这些机制并挑战自己以新的方式思考这些机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198460/extras/c6feb5f178cde8621693c4944f5d290d.poster.avif?t=1734144758\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198460/extras/c6feb5f178cde8621693c4944f5d290d.webm?t=1734144758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198460/extras/c6feb5f178cde8621693c4944f5d290d.mp4?t=1734144758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大量内容：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《元素逻辑》中的所有谜题都是独一无二的，带来了一些新的东西，并且建立在游戏机制的基础上。这使得谜题和秘密感觉很有趣，它们组合在一起形成了完整的谜题体验。</p>",
